data.title: Would You Like to Own the Digital Movie Dune?
data.meta_description: Ooooooh ladies, gentlemen, and everyone in between. If you are in a binging mood let's get you started with a brand new release to add to your movie library!
data.text:
Do you think you would survive the spice?

I have to be honest, I have never seen the original Dune. Shout-out to our local Yakima connection. Did you know that Kyle MacLachlan, the star of the original, was born in Yakima, Washington?

Watching the new version, I was super impressed. I could follow along with the story and I even saw how George Lucas was inspired while creating Star Wars!

What is Dune about?

ONE OF SCIENCE FICTION’S MOST VISIONARY STORIES IS BROUGHT TO LIFE. DUNE’S TIME HAS COME. AND IT’S ONLY THE BEGINNING. TIMOTHY CHALAMET, OSCAR ISAAC, JASON MAMOA, AND ZENDAYA STAR IN DUNE! OWN IT ON DIGITAL NOW AND 4K ULTRA HD JANUARY 11TH!

It's based on a series of books, I have yet to read but wouldn't mind owning as well. Would you like to own your own digital movie of Dune?

Message us via the app or stay tuned for my, Sarah J's, cue to calls between 10 am - 3 pm on-air all this week. This is a first come first serve offer but if you've never used Movies Anywhere. Within 10 minutes of me providing you with your code, you've got the movie available to stream on multiple platforms you already use! Easy peasy and perfect for binging, you don't even need to leave the couch from start to finish, if you didn't want to!

Here's a taste of what is in store for your brand new feature film!

If you don't want to stop at one digital download make sure to let me know and I will dig into the vault to offer up more options as well!
